      "content": "it's not just the name though. i've been watching it and the signal is way stronger when i'm standing in the kitchen vs the living room, and its like it scales perfectly with my movement. i dont think they have \"surveillance software\" like a spy agency, i just mean like, wouldn't someone with a high-gain antenna or some kind of specialized router be able to map out signal strength to see which room someone is in? it feels way too intentional to be a coincidence",
