      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but what if it's not just about being a 'pro' or some spy agency thing? like, wouldn't someone just need a specific setup, maybe some kind of signal triangulation or even just a smart home hub they've rigged up? it's just so weird that they picked that specific phrase as the name. it feels like they're taunting me because they know they can see me. if they were just being trolls, wouldn't they pick something random? this feels targeted. how would someone even set up a system to test that kind of thing without being obvious?",
